    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but is it actually a \"lack of attention to detail\" or is it just a different way of speaking? like, some people talk like that naturally depending on where they're from. wouldn't it be unfair to assume they aren't smart or capable just because they don't use formal grammar? it feels like you're saying one person is better just because they sound more \"standard.\"",
